<p>Your comments, including some <a href="https://make.wordpress.org/meta/2016/12/12/new-homepage-redesign/">feedback from the 2016 redesign</a>, were taken into consideration with this work. Expect more updates to come as efforts to jazz up WordPress.org continue.</p>
